{"tid":2160471,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"個個都可以笑 係得你班臭熱刺迷無資格笑","createTime":"2020-08-17T03:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T09:33:45.000Z","uid":5655,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"79c181f7c02b14ed37e40c0accc21a816b8d4dfc","tid":2160471,"uid":5655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"係 我地係好嬲<br />\n蘇b臨場調動好廢<br />\n但最少我哋打到歐霸盃四強<br />\n只係輸比西維爾一球<br />\n要知道車仔比拜仁大炒<br />\n利物浦晨早出咗局<br />\n鏝連法甲野都輸<br />\n但至小佢哋有為英超付出<br />\n但係熱刺呢？<br />\n一早出晒局<br />\n自己本土聯賽成績又唔掂<br />\n就算搵摩佬返黎教<br />\n都係咁渣<br />\n以前講乜嘢未來隊<br />\n你個簡尼都27歲啦<br />\n我地綠木 拉豬 先係真正既未來<br />\n見到熱刺球迷過嚟差一腳<br />\n真係無名火起"},{"pid":"f9e01c3f069b02c058961fd17183758bb712d341","tid":2160471,"uid":193872,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T03:40:07.000Z","msg":"獌輸波就係人都笑得 有分資唔資格架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4713f7a4c29cdf381591c69f51ff896b509ca2ee","tid":2160471,"uid":104096,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T03:43:47.000Z","msg":"資格論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c72181216177a0393b0ede4cfb8218ff98a6cd","tid":2160471,"uid":38189,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T03:45:10.000Z","msg":"我地熱刺舊年亞軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3bedfcc15bb11020c779a93083a26dd09d3cb6","tid":2160471,"uid":96941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T03:46:20.000Z","msg":"老孫亞洲第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c0a91540361374020ad6cc1be9bf5cb180d080","tid":2160471,"uid":5655,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"d0c72181216177a0393b0ede4cfb8218ff98a6cd","tid":2160471,"uid":38189,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T03:45:10.000Z","msg":"我地熱刺舊年亞軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"rep